comments: Brown (BOS) initiates contact with Mobley?s (CLE) arm during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Smart (BOS) and LeVert (CLE) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Brogdon (BOS) moves alongside Mitchell?s (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) briefly grasps Wade's (CLE) jersey as he attempts to establish post position and the contact is marginal.
Tatum (BOS) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Wade (CLE) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs during his drive.
Horford (BOS) establishes a screening position and does not deliver illegal contact to Wade (CLE) as the screen occurs.
Tatum (BOS) briefly clasps and releases Wade's (CLE) arm as they engage for position off ball and the contact is marginal.
Brown (BOS) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps and the ball becomes loose when it goes off of Wade's (CLE) body.  Brown legally recovers the ball and maintains his pivot foot.
Smart (BOS) shuffles his feet at the start of his dribble.
Brown (BOS) and LeVert (CLE) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Allen (CLE) and Smart (BOS) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound and marginal contact occurs.
LeVert (CLE) initiates some contact with Brown's (BOS) off-arm when it is off of the ball and he moves through the marginal contact to finish at the basket.
Horford (BOS) initiates contact with Allen?s (CLE) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Kornet (BOS) and Mobley (CLE) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Allen (CLE) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Tatum?s (BOS) arm.
Mobley (CLE) brings his hands toward Brown (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as Mobley (CLE) releases away to roll.
Horford (BOS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Kornet (BOS) initiates contact with LeVert?s (CLE) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position just outside of Mitchell's (CLE) path but marginal contact occurs to his front.
Mitchell (CLE) delivers body contact to Smart (BOS) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Kornet (BOS) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and does not deliver illegal contact to LeVert (CLE) during the pick.
Allen (CLE) initiates contact with Brown?s (BOS) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) and Allen (CLE) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound and marginal contact occurs.
LeVert (CLE) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Tatum (BOS) initiates contact with LeVert?s (CLE) arm that affects his SQBR.
Smart (BOS) and Allen (CLE) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
All Flagrant Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
LeVert (CLE) does not get off a shot attempt that touches the rim prior to the shot clock expiring.
